---
import { Card, CardContent } from '../components/ui/card';
---

<section id="about" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-ink/10 py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-display mt-4 text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          Four high school students, one shared vision
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/60">
          <p>
            We created Aveira because we lived the problem. Late-night scrolling, lost sleep,
            groggy mornings. We wanted a real boundary between us and our phones - not another
            app, not a notification setting, but a physical object that changes behavior.
          </p>
          <p>
            Aveira detects your presence in the room using a radar sensor - no camera, no
            microphone. When it knows you're still awake past your set bedtime and your phone
            isn't docked, the alarm goes off. The only way to silence it is to place your
            phone on the dock.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
          <Card class="bg-warm-white">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-accent">4</span>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/50">Students</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card class="bg-warm-white">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-accent">1</span>
              <br />
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/50">Idea</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card class="bg-warm-white">
            <CardContent class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-accent">100%</span>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink/50">Privacy</span>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden border border-ink/10 bg-accent/[0.02] p-6">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-1 w-full bg-accent"></div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">The Mission</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/60">
            Replace the friction of willpower with the finality of a physical object. Every
            detail of Aveira is designed to make better sleep the path of least resistance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
